source.name: Data.gov Dataset Monthly Download Trends
source.description: This dataset provies the trend of downloads in Data.gov. These numbers represent the number of times a user has clicked on the "XML" or "CSV" (for example) links in the Raw Data Catalogs to download datasets and user downloads of tools in the Tool Catalog available in these categories.
